data.meta_description: Raymond first married Floie Maud Keith on Apr. 23, 1903 in Ritchie Co., WV. They had 3 children: Kenneth, Kelcie & Edith Alice. Floie died in 1910.  Raymond's second marriage was to Hazel Virginia (Tanner) Hennen on May 8, 1927. Hazel had a daughter from a previous marriage - Hannah Twilia Hennen. This marriage...
